text: Octavio Mauricio Zapata Possu (born 14 November 1989) is a Colombian footballer who plays as a defender for Aragua F.C. in the Venezuelan Primera División. ==References== Category:Monagas S.C. players Category:Asociación Civil Deportivo Lara players Category:Deportivo Anzoátegui players Category:Aragua FC players Category:Venezuelan Primera División players Category:Colombian footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Sportspeople from Bogotá Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Academia Puerto Cabello players
